About me

I’m a 19 yo french weird student in multimedia with colored hair, some nice tattoos and a little ring in the nose. Passionate about web development and creative design, I do websites, essentially in the domain of creative web development, and more cool stuff.

Since years, I did some design stuff in my free time and as time goes by I hesitated to study design but I thought it wasn't really for me. Some time after that, being a fan of technology and computers, I discover the joys of coding with a few high school's projects. At this time I knew that I wanted to code in the future but not in which domain.

Then I went to university, and boom. Big bang. I started to do websites, first in simple HTML / CSS then with some Javascript, some PHP, etc... Even if I've some facility in back-end development, I fell in love with front-end development and started to learn more on it in my free time (like when I was a kid with design you know).

Finally, I discovered the existence of creative development world and knew what I’m gonna do in my future. I like to discover and learn new stuff about web creative development, and mix my kid's passion with my current passion is something that I really love to do.
